getting and tackle them systematically.

Middleware explained in the Express docs: https://expressjs.com/en/guide/using-middleware.html

For those who want to create a separate frontend to practice using fetch and making requests to your API, 
you'll need to make use of this (third-party) middleware package: https://www.npmjs.com/package/cors
Here is a quick explainer: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PNtFSVU-YTI

